The shaman handing in the epic tear( to trigger aggro) Now people say you are supposed to die when you hand it in but I managed to live.

2 Mage fire pets perferably as close to lvl 60 as possible(I did mine before the PoP)
 2 50-60 clerics for healing.  

This is all it took to down Rak himself I had others with me to help get there but once we got him spawned he  went down rather quick even ch'd himself once.  Near the end we jumped him and finished it off but the fire pets made quick work of him.  

